# KSV014 / readOnlyRootFilesystem: The frontend (Nuxt/Nitro) writes temporary
# files to the container filesystem at runtime. The container runs as non-root
# with all capabilities dropped and seccomp RuntimeDefault applied.
KSV014

# AVD-KSV-01010 / sensitive ConfigMap keys: NITRO_PORT is a TCP port number,
# not a secret. Trivy's heuristic false-positives on the "PORT" substring.
AVD-KSV-01010
